### =========================================================
### 0. 测试前准备：先查账户余额与流水
### =========================================================

### 查询用户1账户
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1

### 查询用户2账户
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/2

### 查询用户1流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1/flows

### 查询用户2流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/2/flows


### =========================================================
### 1. 重复 tradeNo 幂等测试
### 预期：
### - 第一次成功
### - 第二次被幂等拦截或返回重复请求提示
### - trade_order 只有一条
### - 双方余额/流水只变化一次
### =========================================================

### 幂等测试-第一次
POST http://localhost:8083/trades/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tradeNo": "T_REPEAT_202604010001",
  "fromUserId": 1,
  "toUserId": 2,
  "amount": 50.00
}

### 幂等测试-第二次（相同 tradeNo）
POST http://localhost:8083/trades/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tradeNo": "T_REPEAT_202604010001",
  "fromUserId": 1,
  "toUserId": 2,
  "amount": 50.00
}

### 查询交易单
GET http://localhost:8083/trades/T_REPEAT_202604010001

### 查询用户1流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1/flows

### 查询用户2流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/2/flows


